Create a Keyword Action Class with all the action keyword methods/user actions/steps user doing on the page.
Create a Test Excel with Test Case Name/ID, Test Step ID, Descriptions, ActionKeywords which user is performing on the page to complete the Test.
Create a Excel Utility to Read the excel
Create a Test Class/Driver Class/Execution Engine to perform the test steps by reading the excel action keyword column
The only idea behind the Keyword Driven framework is to accept the action keywords from the Excel, so that all the test cases can be easily created in Excel file.
Refection Classes - Reflection is a very useful approach to deal with the Java class at runtime as it can be used to load the Java class, call its methods or analysis the class at runtime.